OL,3,CCompany fined after dad's leg is
OL,4,Camputated after being crushed by pallet
OL,6,FA manufacturer in Sheffield has been
OL,7,Ffined #60,000 after an employee who
OL,8,Fwas crushed by a steel pallet had to
OL,9,Fhave his leg amputated.
OL,11,FWayne Hatton, from Doncaster, was
OL,12,Fworking a night shift at Amber Precast
OL,13,FLtd's factory on 14 January 2021 when
OL,14,Fthe 800kg load fell onto the father-of-
OL,15,Ftwo, who had only recently been
OL,16,Femployed by the firm as a supervisor.
