OL,3,CCompany fined after dad's leg is
OL,4,Camputated after being crushed by pallet
OL,6,FMr Hatton spent seven weeks in
OL,7,Fhospital and had his right lower leg
OL,8,Famputated and two toes on his left
OL,9,Ffoot removed following the incident at
OL,10,FDavy Business Park. He now uses a
OL,11,Fprosthetic leg.
OL,13,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,14,Finvestigation found the pallet had not
OL,15,Fbeen secured onto the lifting chains
OL,16,Fof the overhead crane before being
OL,17,Fremoved from a concrete cast.
