OL,3,CCompany fined after dad's leg is
OL,4,Camputated after being crushed by pallet
OL,6,FThe investigation also found Amber
OL,7,FPrecast Ltd failed to consistently
OL,8,Fimplement a system of work to ensure
OL,9,Fthe pallet could be removed safely. Mr
OL,10,FHatton and other members of his team
OL,11,Fhad not received any information or
OL,12,Finstructions on how to remove the
OL,13,Fpallet safely.
OL,15,FAmber Precast Ltd, of Davy Business
OL,16,FPark in Sheffield, was fined #60,000
OL,17,Fand ordered to pay over #5,000 in
OL,18,Fcosts at Sheffield Magistrates' Court.
