OL,3,CCompany fined after dad's leg is
OL,4,Camputated after being crushed by pallet
OL,6,FHSE inspector Jane Fox said: "This
OL,7,Fincident could so easily have been
OL,8,Favoided with the correct instruction
OL,9,Fand implementation of an agreed safe
OL,10,Fworking procedure. Amber Precast Ltd
OL,11,Fleft its employees to work out their
OL,12,Fown methods of completing the pallet
OL,13,Fremoval task, instead of providing
OL,14,Fthem with suitable training and
OL,15,Fequipment so it could be done safely
OL,16,Fevery time."
